<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Shaheer | Personal Portfolio</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Shaheer - Web Developer / Designer / Creator from Lahore"/>
  
  <!-- Google Fonts (optional - remove if you want zero external requests) -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f17;
      color: #e0e0ff;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    a { color: #00d4ff; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* Header / Hero */
    header {
      height: 100vh;
      min-height: 600px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f17 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff, #a78bfa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #a0a0cc;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .social-links a {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin: 0 1rem;
      color: #a0a0cc;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
      color: #00d4ff;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: #00d4ff;
      color: #0f0f17;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 50px;
      margin: 0.5rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      border: 2px solid #00d4ff;
      color: #00d4ff;
    }

    /* Sections */
    section {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: #00d4ff;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: #1a1a2e;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid #333366;
      transition: all 0.4s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      border-color: #00d4ff;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
    }

    .card h3 {
      color: #00d4ff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    /* Projects */
    .project-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 220px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
      color: #666699;
      border-top: 1px solid #222244;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; }
      .hero p  { font-size: 1.2rem; }
      section   { padding: 70px 0; }
      h2        { font-size: 2.4rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container hero">
      <h1>Hi, I'm Shaheer</h1>
      <p>Web Enthusiast • Problem Solver • Based in Lahore</p>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/YOUR-USERNAME" target="_blank">Twitter / X</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/YOUR-PROFILE" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <a href="#projects" class="btn">See My Work</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Who I Am</h3>
          <p>I'm a passionate self-taught developer from Lahore who loves building clean, fast, and user-friendly websites and apps. Currently exploring frontend, UI/UX, and a bit of everything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>What I Do</h3>
          <p>HTML • CSS • JavaScript • React • Tailwind • Git • Responsive Design • GitHub Pages magic ✨</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>My Goal</h3>
          <p>To create things that make life simpler, prettier, or just more fun — one line of code at a time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="projects" style="background:#0a0a1a;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>My Projects</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <!-- Replace with real screenshot links later -->
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/1a1a2e/00d4ff?text=Project+1" alt="Project 1" class="project-img">
          <h3>Project One</h3>
          <p>A cool web app / website description goes here. Built with HTML, CSS, JS.</p>
          <p><a href="#">Live Demo</a> • <a href="#">Source Code</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/1a1a2e/00d4ff?text=Project+2" alt="Project 2" class="project-img">
          <h3>Project Two</h3>
          <p>Another awesome thing I built — maybe a game, tool, or landing page.</p>
          <p><a href="#">Live Demo</a> • <a href="#">Source Code</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/1a1a2e/00d4ff?text=Project+3" alt="Project 3" class="project-img">
          <h3>Project Three</h3>
          <p>Describe your third coolest project here :)</p>
          <p><a href="#">Live Demo</a> • <a href="#">Source Code</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
      <div style="text-align:center; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto;">
        <p style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">
          Want to collaborate, ask a question, or just say hi?<br>
          Drop me a message anytime!
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" class="btn" style="font-size:1.3rem; padding:18px 40px;">
          Send Email →
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:3rem; color:#8888aa;">
          Or find me on socials above ↑
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 Shaheer — Made with ♡ & GitHub Pages</p>
  </footer>

  <!-- Optional: smooth scroll for anchor links -->
  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
      anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
          behavior: 'smooth'
        });
      });
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>
